extendedInfo.description: Android app to practice your knowledge before taking the Written Test part of Texas Driver License Test.

reviews.title: Pretty decent app
reviews.comment: It\'s pretty good but I beleive there\'s a few errors. The one I noticed was the question about urban areas. Your answer says 20 mph limit but the book says 30 mph and Google shows 15-30 mph. Another thing that\'d make this better is to add a random question generator, like use the 120 questions at the back of the handbook.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Needs improvement.
reviews.comment: A question in set 3 has an incorrect answer as being the correct answer.  Hint - The urban speed limit in Texas is 30 MPH.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Great!
reviews.comment: Its surprisingly accurate and as three practice tests for a total of 30 questions. I passed my test easily and this test helped.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Cool.
reviews.comment: This app actually helped me. I\'m glad that I downloaded it. Highly recommend
reviews.author: A Google User
